PROSPECT FINANCE SAAS TEMPLATE - COMPLETE COLOR PALETTE
========================================================

Template: Prospect by Medium Rare
URL: https://prospect-finance-saas-webflow-template.webflow.io/
Design Philosophy: Retro-inspired glassmorphic aesthetic with balanced neutral palette

================================================================================

1. PRIMARY BRAND COLORS
================================================================================

┌──────────────────┬─────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│     Color        │   Hex Code  │                  Usage                      │
├──────────────────┼─────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Dark             │  #0D0D0D    │ Primary logo, headings, body text           │
│                  │  (Est.)     │ Navigation text, footer text on light BG    │
├──────────────────┼─────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Dark Charcoal    │  #1A1A1A    │ Secondary dark, card backgrounds (dark)     │
│                  │  (Est.)     │ Dark section backgrounds                    │
└──────────────────┴─────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────┘

Note: "Dark" is the primary brand color referenced throughout the template.
The exact shade appears to be a near-black charcoal optimized for legibility.


