14. CSS VARIABLE MAPPING (RECOMMENDED)
================================================================================

--color-dark: #0D0D0D;
--color-dark-charcoal: #1A1A1A;
--color-light-1: #F5F5F5;
--color-light-2: #EBEBEB;
--color-white: #FFFFFF;

--color-accent-purple: #5A26F0;
--color-accent-red: #F04343;

--color-gray-900: #1A1A1A;
--color-gray-700: #4A4A4A;
--color-gray-500: #737373;
--color-gray-300: #B3B3B3;
--color-gray-100: #E5E5E5;

--color-border-light: #E5E5E5;
--color-border-subtle: rgba(13, 13, 13, 0.12);
--color-border-focus: #5A26F0;

--color-success: #22C55E;
--color-warning: #F59E0B;
--color-info: #3B82F6;
--color-error: #F04343;

--color-star: #FBBF24;


