NOTES ON DATA SOURCES
================================================================================

CONFIRMED VALUES (from official sources):
- Purple accent: #5A26F0 (Medium Rare shop page - form validation)
- Red error: #F04343 (Medium Rare shop page - form validation)
- Dark/Light logo variants documented in style guide

ESTIMATED VALUES (derived from visual inspection and common patterns):
- All gray scale values (Est.)
- Background colors (Est.)
- Status colors except error (Est.)

The template uses a sophisticated neutral palette optimized for:
- Finance/legal/consulting professional services
- High legibility and accessibility
- Modern glassmorphic aesthetic
- Retro-inspired typography contrast

